<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<%- include('partials/head', { title, description, canonicalUrl, ogImage, structuredData, site }) %>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav', { active: 'about', site }) %>

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="page-hero-bg">
            <picture>
                <source srcset="/images/hero-armed-response.webp?v=<%= assetVersion %>" type="image/webp">
                <img src="/images/hero-armed-response.jpg?v=<%= assetVersion %>" alt="MJP Security patrol vehicles on duty at a Cape Town home at night" fetchpriority="high">
            </picture>
            <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <p class="hero-eyebrow">ABOUT MJP SECURITY</p>
            <h1 class="page-title">YOUR COMMUNITY ARMED RESPONSE SERVICE</h1>
            <div class="title-bar"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about about-page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-block about-who">
                    <h2 class="section-title">WHO WE ARE</h2>
                    <div class="title-bar"></div>
                    <p>MJP Security Services is a proudly South African security company committed to delivering professional, reliable, and customer-focused security solutions to businesses, residential communities, government institutions, and private clients.</p>
                    <p>We operate with integrity, professionalism, accountability, and excellence, and we work to create safer environments through highly trained personnel, modern security practices, and a proactive approach to risk management. We understand that every client has unique security requirements, which is why we provide tailored security solutions designed to protect people, property, and assets.</p>
                    <p>At MJP Security, we believe that security is more than just a service — it's a commitment to protecting what matters most. Our management team and security personnel are dedicated to upholding the highest standards of professionalism, compliance, and customer service while building long-term partnerships grounded in trust and reliability.</p>
                    <p>Whether protecting homes, businesses, industrial sites, retail centres, or special events, MJP Security Services remains committed to delivering security solutions that provide confidence, peace of mind, and exceptional value to every client.</p>
                    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary mt-2">CONTACT US</a>
                </div>

                <div class="about-image-wrap">
                    <div class="about-image-inner">
                        <div class="about-badge">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            <span>PSIRA<br>Registered</span>
                        </div>
                        <picture>
                            <source srcset="/images/about-team.webp?v=<%= assetVersion %>" type="image/webp">
                            <img src="/images/about-team.jpg?v=<%= assetVersion %>" alt="MJP Security PSIRA-registered security officer" loading="lazy" width="240" height="240">
                        </picture>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-block about-commitment">
                    <h2 class="section-title">ABOUT US</h2>
                    <div class="title-bar"></div>
                    <p>With a strong commitment to protecting lives, property, and assets, we deliver tailored security services that meet the unique needs of every client. Our experienced management team and highly trained security personnel work proactively to prevent crime, manage risks, and ensure a safe and secure environment at all times.</p>
                    <p>Our footprint covers Cape Town's Northern and Southern suburbs.</p>
                    <div class="commitment-pillars">
                        <div class="pillar"><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i><span>Integrity</span></div>
                        <div class="pillar"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i><span>Accountability</span></div>
                        <div class="pillar"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i><span>Excellence</span></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why-us">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-heading-center">
                <h2 class="section-title">WHY CHOOSE US?</h2>
                <div class="title-bar center"></div>
                <p class="section-sub">We are passionate about our business and our customers, and truly understand that happy customers are what keeps us in business.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="why-us-grid">
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                    <h3>Professional &amp; Highly Trained Personnel</h3>
                    <p>Our security officers are carefully selected, professionally trained, and committed to delivering exceptional service with integrity and discipline.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
                    <h3>Tailored Security Solutions</h3>
                    <p>We understand that every client has unique security needs. We develop customised security strategies that provide effective protection for your people, property, and assets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    <h3>24/7 Protection</h3>
                    <p>Our team is available around the clock to provide continuous monitoring, rapid response, and dependable security services whenever you need us.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                    <h3>Customer-Focused Approach</h3>
                    <p>We build long-term relationships by providing responsive communication, reliable service, and security solutions that exceed client expectations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
                    <h3>Experienced Management Team</h3>
                    <p>Our leadership brings industry knowledge, operational expertise, and hands-on management to ensure every contract is professionally managed.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
                    <h3>Modern Security Practices</h3>
                    <p>We combine skilled personnel with proven security procedures and technology to deliver effective and proactive security solutions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                    <h3>Rapid Response Capability</h3>
                    <p>Our response teams are trained to react quickly and professionally to security incidents, helping minimise risk and protect your assets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i>
                    <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
                    <p>Regular site inspections, supervision, and performance monitoring ensure we consistently maintain the highest standards of service.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
                    <h3>Comprehensive Security Services</h3>
                    <p>From guarding and armed response to CCTV monitoring, VIP protection, event security, and security training, we provide complete security solutions under one trusted brand.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="why-us-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                    <h3>Commitment to Excellence</h3>
                    <p>At MJP Security, we are driven by professionalism, accountability, integrity, and continuous improvement, ensuring every client receives dependable service and complete peace of mind.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stats-grid mt-3">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <span class="stat-num">24/7</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">Active Protection</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <span class="stat-num">16</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">Services Offered</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <span class="stat-num">100%</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">PSIRA Registered</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <span class="stat-num">CPT</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">North &amp; South Suburbs</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-strip">
        <div class="container cta-inner">
            <div>
                <h2 class="section-title">READY TO SECURE YOUR HOME OR BUSINESS?</h2>
                <p>Get a free consultation and quote from our team — standing by 24/7.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-actions">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">REQUEST A QUOTE</a>
                <a href="tel:<%= site.phoneHref %>" class="btn-outline"><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> <%= site.phoneDisplay %></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<%- include('partials/footer', { site }) %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
